TimeString(),\n            isUser: false\n          });\n        }, 1000);\n      }\n    }\n  }\n};","map":{"version":3,"names":["NavbarPusat","components","data","searchQuery","selectedCategory","categories","newsList","Array","keys","map","i","id","title","description","tanggalPublikasi","kategori","image","pengunjung","Math","floor","random","currentPage","itemsPerPage","news","relatedNews","showChat","newMessage","messages","text","time","Date","toLocaleTimeString","isUser","computed","filteredNews","filter","toLowerCase","includes","totalPages","ceil","length","methods","sendMessage","trim","push","setTimeout"],"sources":["C:\\Users\\IMAM\\OneDrive\\Desktop\\LPKNI\\lpkniweb\\src\\views\\pusat\\PortalBeritaPusatView.vue"],"sourcesContent":["<template>\r\n  <div class=\"w-screen bg-gray-100\">\r\n    \r\n    <NavbarPusat/>\r\n    \r\n    <!-- Search Bar -->\r\n    <div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex justify-between items-center\">\r\n      <input v-model=\"searchQuery\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Cari berita...\" class=\"w-2/3 p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#03a980]\" />\r\n      <select v-model=\"selectedCategory\" class=\"p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#03a980]\">\r\n        <option value=\"\">Semua Kategori</option>\r\n        <option v-for=\"cat in categories\" :key=\"cat\" :value=\"cat\">{{ cat }}</option>\r\n      </select>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <!-- Container utama dengan layout Tribunnews -->\r\n    <div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto py-6 px-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\r\n      \r\n      <!-- Kolom Utama (Berita Terbaru) -->\r\n      <div class=\"md:col-span-2\">\r\n        <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#028a66] border-b-4 border-[#03a980] pb-2 mb-6\">Berita Terbaru</h2>\r\n        \r\n        <div v-for=\"news in filteredNews\" :key=\"news.id\" class=\"flex items-center bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-4\">\r\n          <img :src=\"news.image\" alt=\"Gambar Berita\" class=\"w-32 h-32 object-cover rounded-md mr-4\">\r\n          <div>\r\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-[#333]\">{{ news.title }}</h3>\r\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-[#4f4f4f]\">{{ news.description.substring(0, 100) }}...</p>\r\n            <span class=\"text-xs text-[#028a66]\">{{ news.kategori }} â€¢ {{ news.tanggalPublikasi }}</span>\r\n            <a :href=\"`/news/${news.id}`\" class=\"text-[#0090ff] hover:text-[#028a66] text-sm font-medium block mt-2\">Baca Selengkapnya</a>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <!-- Sidebar (Rekomendasi dan Popular) -->\r\n      <div>\r\n        <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#028a66] border-b-4 border-[#03a980] pb-2 mb-4\">Rekomendasi</h2>\r\n        \r\n        <div v-for=\"news in filteredNews.slice(0, 5)\" :key=\"news.id\" class=\"mb-4\">\r\n          <a :href=\"`/news/${news.id}`\" class=\"flex items-center\">\r\n            <img :src=\"news.image\" alt=\"Gambar Berita\" class=\"w-20 h-20 object-cover rounded-md mr-3\">\r\n            <p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-[#333]\">{{ news.title }}</p>\r\n          </a>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <!-- Pagination -->\r\n    <div class=\"flex justify-center items-center mt-8 space-x-2\">\r\n      <button @click=\"prevPage\" :disabled=\"currentPage === 1\" class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-[#03a980] text-white rounded-md hover:bg-[#028a66] disabled:opacity-50\">Previous</button>\r\n      <button v-for=\"page in totalPages\" :key=\"page\" @click=\"currentPage = page\" class=\"px-4 py-2 border rounded-md\" :class=\"currentPage === page ? 'bg-[#03a980] text-white' : 'bg-white text-black hover:bg-gray-200'\">{{ page }}</button>\r\n      <button @click=\"nextPage\" :disabled=\"currentPage === totalPages\" class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-[#03a980] text-white rounded-md hover:bg-[#028a66] disabled:opacity-50\">Next</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"fixed bottom-6 right-6\">\r\n      <button @click=\"showChat = true\" class=\"bg-[#03a980] p-4 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-[#028a66] transition\">\r\n        ðŸ’¬\r\n      </button>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <!-- Chat Modal -->\r\n    <div v-if=\"showChat\" class=\"fixed bottom-20 right-6 w-[350px] bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg border border-gray-300 z-50\">\r\n      <div class=\"flex justify-between items-center bg-[#03a980] text-white px-4 py-3 rounded-t-lg\">\r\n        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold\">Chat dengan customerservices</h3>\r\n        <button @click=\"showChat = false\" class=\"text-xl\">&times;</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"p-4 h-[300px] overflow-y-auto\" ref=\"chatContainer\">\r\n        <div v-for=\"(message, index) in messages\" :key=\"index\" class=\"mb-3 flex\" :class=\"{'justify-end': message.isUser}\">\r\n          <div class=\"max-w-[75%] p-2 rounded-lg shadow\" :class=\"message.isUser ? 'bg-[#03a980] text-white' : 'bg-gray-100'\">\r\n            <p class=\"text-sm\">{{ message.text }}</p>\r\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1 text-right\">{{ message.time }}</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"flex p-3 border-t\">\r\n        <input v-model=\"newMessage\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Ketik pesan...\" class=\"flex-grow px-3 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:ring-[#03a980]\" @keyup.enter=\"sendMessage\" />\r\n        <button @click=\"sendMessage\" class=\"ml-2 px-4 py-2 bg-[#03a980] text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-[#028a66]\">Kirim</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n  </div>\r\n</template>\r\n\r\n<script>\r\n\r\nimport NavbarPusat from '@/components/NavbarPusat.vue';\r\n\r\nexport default {  \r\n  components: {\r\n    NavbarPusat\r\n  },\r\n  data() {\r\n    return {\r\n      searchQuery: '',\r\n      selectedCategory: '',\r\n      categories: ['Politik', 'Olahraga', 'Teknologi', 'Nasional', 'Internasional'],\r\n      newsList: [...Array(20).keys()].map(i => ({\r\n        id: i + 1,\r\n        title: `Judul Berita ${i + 1}`,\r\n        description: `Deskripsi berita nomor ${i + 1}`,\r\n        tanggalPublikasi: `2024-02-${(i % 28) + 1}`,\r\n        kategori: ['Politik', 'Olahraga', 'Teknologi', 'Nasional', 'Internasional'][i % 5],\r\n        image: 'http://local',\r\n        pengunjung: Math.floor(Math.random() * (5000 - 1000 + 1)) + 1000 \r\n      })),\r\n      currentPage: 1,\r\n      itemsPerPage: 5,\r\n      news: {},\r\n      relatedNews: [],\r\n      showChat: false,\r\n      newMessage: \"\",\r\n      messages: [{ text: \"Halo! Ada yang bisa dibantu?\", time: new Date().toLocaleTimeString(), isUser: false }]\r\n    };\r\n  },\r\n  computed: {\r\n    filteredNews() {\r\n      return this.newsList.filter(news => \r\n        news.title.toLowerCase().includes(this.searchQuery.toLowerCase()) && \r\n        (this.selectedCategory ? news.kategori === this.selectedCategory : true)\r\n      );\r\n    },\r\n    totalPages() {\r\n      return Math.ceil(this.filteredNews.length / this.itemsPerPage);\r\n    }\r\n  },\r\n  methods: {\r\n    sendMessage() {\r\n      if (this.newMessage.trim() !== \"\") {\r\n        this.messages.push({ text: this.newMessage, time: new Date().toLocaleTimeString(), isUser: true });\r\n        this.newMessage = \"\";\r\n        setTimeout(() => {\r\n          this.messages.push({ text: \"Admin sedang online, harap tunggu sebentar.\", time: new Date().toLocaleTimeString(), isUser: false });\r\n        }, 1000);\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n};\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n"],"mappings":";;;;AAkFA,OAAOA,WAAU,MAAO,8BAA8B;AAEtD,eAAe;EACbC,UAAU,EAAE;IACVD;EACF,CAAC;EACDE,IAAIA,CAAA,EAAG;IACL,OAAO;MACLC,WAAW,EAAE,EAAE;MACfC,gBAAgB,EAAE,EAAE;MACpBC,UAAU,EAAE,CAAC,SAAS,EAAE,UAAU,EAAE,WAAW,EAAE,UAAU,EAAE,eAAe,CAAC;MAC7EC,QAAQ,EAAE,CAAC,GAAGC,KAAK,CAAC,EAAE,CAAC,CAACC,IAAI,CAAC,CAAC,CAAC,CAACC,GAAG,CAACC,CAAA,KAAM;QACxCC,EAAE,EAAED,CAAA,GAAI,CAAC;QACTE,KAAK,EAAE,gBAAgBF,CAAA,GAAI,CAAC,EAAE;QAC9BG,WAAW,EAAE,0BAA0BH,CAAA,GAAI,CAAC,EAAE;QAC9CI,gBAAgB,EAAE,WAA